$ SAS data step: file handling

{ Copying a file #sas-data-step-copy-file

  With a combination of → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/statements/infile and
  → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/statements/file, a file can be copied within
  a → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/data-step[data step].

  gh|about-SAS|/programming/data-step/file/copy-file.sas||

  See also → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/files/File-data-buffer/index#sas-fdb-copy-bytewise[Bytewise copy of a file],
  → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/statements/put#sas-put-_infile_[put _infile_].

}
